{"type": "article", "id": 33638, "title": "Marni 创始人卸任创意总监，以及，Beams40周年鞋款不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-10-24T02:52:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 22268, "name": "Clarks Originals"}, {"id": 26308, "name": "Veja"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 34214, "name": "Reigning Champ"}, {"id": 34215, "name": "Nonnative"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 8084, "name": "Marni"}, {"id": 20325, "name": "Allure"}, {"id": 23652, "name": "Becca"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161024094552RC3egu84hUB2Itfv.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/burberry-shares-gain-after-report-coach-is-considering-merger\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coach 或将与 Burberry 合并</a>？</b>&nbsp;| 此前，根据金融博客<a href=\"https://www.betaville.co.uk/news/coach-and-blackstone-said-to-be-in-the-early-stages-on-evaluating-8-billion-burberry-bid-sources/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Betaville </a>的消息，Coach 正在计划与 Burberry 合并，此消息一出，Burberry 的股价迅速上涨了 4.8%。不过，有知情人士称，此消息纯属空穴来风。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/article/marni-appoints-francesco-risso-as-creative-director\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Marni 创始人卸任创意总监</b></a> | 作为创始人，Consuelo Castiglioni 宣布卸任意大利品牌 Marni 的创意总监。9 月米兰时装周上所发布的 2017 春夏系列是她在任 20 年所负责的最后一个系列。同时，Marni 母集团 OTB 宣布任命 Francesco Risso 为新的创意总监，Risso 曾效力于  Anna Molinari、Malo 与 Prada 等品牌。&nbsp;</p><p><font color=\"#333332\"><a href=\"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20161021005150/en/Est%C3%A9e-Lauder-Companies-Acquire-BECCA-Cosmetics\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛集团收购当红彩妆品牌 Becca Cosmetics</b></a> |<a href=\"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20161021005150/en/Est%C3%A9e-Lauder-Companies-Acquire-BECCA-Cosmetics\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a>Becca 专营高档美妆产品，在 2013 年被美妆品牌的投资公司 Luxury Brand Partners 收购。</font><font color=\"#333332\">2016 年，Becca Cosmetics 的净销售额预计为 8000 万美元。据业内人士估计，雅诗兰黛的这笔收购，可能高达 2.3 亿美元。</font></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/mens-designer-luxury/raf-simons-show-new-york-fashion-week-mens-10681073/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Raf Simons 要参加 2017 秋冬纽约男装周 </b></a>| Raf Simons 的设计师个人同名品牌将首次登陆纽约男装周。作为全球时尚界最具影响力的设计师之一，Raf Simons 在八月被正式任命为 Calvin Klein 的创意总监。不过，CFDA 美国时尚设计师协会目前尚未公布 Raf Simons 个人品牌的具体发布时间和地点。</p><h3><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 冬青黑, STXihei, 华文细黑, 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, 'Arial sans-serif'; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\">一些值得一看的：</span></h3><p class=\"\">加拿大针织品牌&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/reigning-champ-x-adidas-men-women-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reigning Champ与 adidas 推联名款男装女装系列</a>，这次合作也是 Reigning Champ 首次涉足女装。该系列将 Reigning Champ 的简约风格注入到 adidas 的经典运动服装中，adidas 革新性产品 Zero Negative Energy 连帽衫也由全网眼面料打造。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093701ibgXTdBW1yP4fUqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093714okswiv4ElzB8HNur.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093723VCyuX95aD2YzjQZT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093732NGneEiBxjs4KWAoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>日本时尚集合店 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/beams-x-clarks-originals-desert-trek\" rel=\"nofollow\">BEAMS 40 周年</a>，带来了多款联名系列。这双来自英伦经典品牌  Clarks Originals 的  Desert Trek 鞋款就是一例。这双鞋包括经典的卡其色和黑色，以上乘的麂皮搭配橡胶鞋底。现已登陆 BEAMS 门店。</p><p class=\"\"><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093547rx8i4HAIX76zk5je.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610240936238SEbivKq9mZAoItG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093636o1XWd0v78yps5OcR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093646MSeuUdKzogFZbqxm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Nonnative 是日本设计师藤井隆行于 1999 年创立的个人服装品牌，成立之初即以 In a serene attitude with life 为设计理念。日前，它<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/nonnative-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">公开了 2017 春夏系列 lookbook</a>，这一季的灵感来自于威尼斯南部小城市 Ancona，以当地的自然元素为灵感，结合了军事和户外风格。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093307nOvsKFr8JlaI6y9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093307iAbyt6eP81QuhEYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093307DOkjKfFR7SvAta61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093307qbz4ZCDSIv8XcFBL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093316wyMerOD7Q2dNkYWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093316dhvXjWxV95butTp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024093321AWrt2eN6dl7Cvbmq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Amanda Seyfried 登上了 Allure 杂志十一月刊封面。这组大片由 Scott Trindle 掌镜，Amanda 身上的衣服来自比利时设计师 Dries Van Noten 的设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024101757ti154oGbpQMuZ0zn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024101808sdxf6tAlz1Bq3HZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.385000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024101817q6dSpQu0fb9EvlZT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.272500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024101825XUFjvW4pN0MRZg5A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.360000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}